#
# build API - InfoMetis controplane
#
# The build API consists of one method that builds the repository container image.
#   no flags   : builds the image defined at the current repository node
#   --all      : build the images defined on the current repository node and all child nodes
#   --external : build all images that require external access to build
#   --internal : build all images which require no external access to build
#
